lead_paragraph: Midfielder Cesc Fabregas insists he can play a key role for Chelsea after scoring an extra-time brace to help the Blues knock Premier League champions Leicester City out of the League Cup on Tuesday.

headline.print_headline: Cup Hero Fabregas Ready to Step Up for Chelsea
